
<h3>题意<h3>
<p>给出一个BST，需要把这个tree convert成为，每个node都是当前node的值，加上<p>

<h3>解题<h3>
<p>本质是在考察，一种顺序的tree traversal的形式：
需要先递归右子数，然后进行当前值的变动，然后去递归到左子数<p>

<h3>细节<h3>
<p>sum的使用形式：self.sum<p>


```python
# Definition for a binary tree node.
# class TreeNode(object):
#     def __init__(self, x):
#         self.val = x
#         self.left = None
#         self.right = None

class Solution(object):
    def convertBST(self, root):
        """
        :type root: TreeNode
        :rtype: TreeNode
        """
        self.sum = 0
        self.helper(root)
        return root
    
    def helper(self,root):
        if root is not None:
            self.helper(root.right)
            root.val += self.sum
            self.sum = root.val
            self.helper(root.left)
```
